# Environment (linked VProject)

SSOT: WorkStation `shared/protocols/environment_protocol.md` + `shared/environment_enforcement.yaml`.

- **Install / test / lint / build** only via `bash scripts/dev.sh …` or `docker compose run …`
- **Never** run `npm install`, `npm test`, `npm run`, `pip install`, or bare `vitest` on the host
- **Dev stack** via WorkStation `scripts/dev-env.sh up --project <name>` (main slot) — not host app servers
- Branch/session slots (`ws-{project}-{slot}`) are ephemeral — torn down when the dev session completes
